credit_line: Bequest of Mrs. Charles Denison Makepeace, Class of 1900
title: Untitled: Gloucester, Massachusetts
inscriptions: in plate l.l.: Kuper 27; l.l. in pencil: R.Kuper 27; verso c. in ink: Dear Mr. Makepeace,/ With our New Year's, greetings, please accept/ this little scene of Gloucester/ in your own Massachusetts./ Rose Kuper/ (Mrs. Theodore Fred)/ January 1, 1931/ To Mr. Charles D. Makepeace.
